headline: Stock Index Futures Gain on Fed Rate-Cut Optimism, U.S. Economic Data on Tap
summary: December S&P 500 E-Mini futures (ESZ25) are up +0.34%, and December Nasdaq 100 E-Mini futures (NQZ25) are up +0.42% this morning, buoyed by rising expectations for a Federal Reserve rate cut next month, while investors await a new round of U.S. economic data.

headline: Keysight Technologies (KEYS) Is Up 11.9% After Earnings Beat and $1.5 Billion Buyback Announcement
summary: On November 24, 2025, Keysight Technologies reported fourth-quarter and full-year results with revenue of US$1.42 billion for Q4 and US$5.38 billion for the year, alongside authorizing a new US$1.5 billion share repurchase program and providing above-consensus guidance for Q1 2026. Management's confidence was reflected not only in the share buyback but also in major product launches and new partnerships, signaling ongoing investment in innovation and growth opportunities for the...
